# Epic 4: Backend CRUD Operations
**Status:** Depends on Epic 2 & 3 | **Arch Ref:** Section 4.2 (API Spec)

## Technical Blueprint
- **Payloads:** Strictly JSON. 
- **Validation:** Block requests missing `name` or `user_role`.

## Stories & Specs
### 4.1 POST /api/items
- **Spec:** Payload `{ "name": "Bamba", "user_role": "KID" }`. 
- **AC:** Item is saved to DB with status `PENDING`. Returns 201.

### 4.2 GET /api/items
- **AC:** Returns JSON array of all items.

### 4.3 PUT /api/items/<id>
- **Spec:** Payload `{ "status": "APPROVED" }`. 
- **AC:** Updates status in DB; blocks illegal status transitions.
